{"tid":479410,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"支持茶記等如支持港獨","createTime":"2017-11-25T05:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T11:20:11.000Z","uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f00f93a0682a72e9fa9a4585418d8c11d7a4f45b","tid":479410,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff8a836a20e93c82438064cf673dc25d2e89c14","tid":479410,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4375eac31872c057c160e8f49ae3b7aa73b623","tid":479410,"uid":158660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c13dbbdfdcb02072752f58f6087a0ff2de9363c","tid":479410,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">癲狗廚子自爆肥到要靠照鏡先望到自己條賓周仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">癲狗廚子因為體形肥胖，肚腩太大，企直向下望都被肚腩擋著視線而看不到自己的陰莖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/102117_763c7326006224b881641249396bdd81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F102117_763c7326006224b881641249396bdd81.jpg&h=66f16e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/104258_868815935848ed9730acf2dc780f3a42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F104258_868815935848ed9730acf2dc780f3a42.jpg&h=bfe5c594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/104308_b8696b8727f7a7979661178cdd052a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F104308_b8696b8727f7a7979661178cdd052a55.jpg&h=0b45fb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n癲狗廚子口快快不小心承認這個殘酷事實，並自爆平常需要靠照鏡才能看到自己陰莖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/102131_16c392a200d040643a26208a3e22a6d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F102131_16c392a200d040643a26208a3e22a6d1.jpg&h=91762ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常男人向下望便可看到自己的陰莖，癲狗廚子卻教別人照鏡，不慎爆出自己的習慣。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哎喲喲，陰功咯，癲狗廚子原來肥到見唔到自己條賓周仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59e168bc413503cddfeb6550e73286e7180d8bb","tid":479410,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>陰功得過你條傻鳩? 睇下你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/2hx06o3i3j/1507948730452.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F2hx06o3i3j%2F1507948730452.png&h=24ca1f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正常男人望下面就望到自己賓周，但你睇下自己幾撚大個肚腩，本癲狗好心，建議下你照鏡等自己睇到粒賓周仔，點知原來你條傻鳩唔識中文衝出黎柒:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/324dmgopy7/Screenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F324dmgopy7%2FScreenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png&h=a28273a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>肥鳩大隻連解讀中文&ldquo;你照鏡咪知囉懵撚&rdquo;哩句句子都有困難，自己柒左仲要周圍話俾人知，不如學好d中文先出黎教人啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></span></span>"},{"pid":"26a96b9a8dee8af80910ece22b52ea66d1cf7b95","tid":479410,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衲dee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8bcee95ee344fe091b9dda2c57f881a9801acc","tid":479410,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be025497c81ab1525830e61ad61886236fbc443b","tid":479410,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}